jjil.core
Class ErrorCodes

java.lang.Object
  jjil.core.ErrorCodes

public class ErrorCodes
extends java.lang.Object

Define error codes specific to the jjil.core library. Other libraries define their own codes in their own ErrorCodes object.

J2ME's version of Java doesn't support enums. So we simulate them using an old trick...
